dct_title_s: A survey of the keys and shoals in the Mira-por-vos Passage
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Includes inset view of rocks as seen from the western side of the passage. "408." Historic Maps copy has label on verso: Bahamas. Mira-por-vos Passage. 408.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographical Office of the Admiralty, 29th. Feby. 1828.
